### Roles Defined in `User.roles` Enum

`student`, `faculty`, `caretaker`, `coach`, `executive`, [admin](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/controllers/subscriptionControllerV2.js#115-181), `coordinator`, `gym_admin`, `swim_admin`

> **Note:** Users have an **array** of roles — a single user can hold multiple roles simultaneously.

### Business Rules in Code

| Rule | Location | Detail |
|------|----------|--------|
| Fair-use quota | [bookingService.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/services/bookingService.js) | Max 2 active bookings in 72-hour rolling window |
| No-show penalty | [penaltyService.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/services/penaltyService.js) | 3 no-shows in 30 days → 7-day suspension |
| Late cancel penalty | [penaltyService.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/services/penaltyService.js) | 2 late cancellations in 30 days → 7-day suspension |
| Late cancel threshold | [bookingControllerV2.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/controllers/bookingControllerV2.js) | Cancel < 2 hours before slot = late cancel |
| Check-in window | [bookingControllerV2.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/controllers/bookingControllerV2.js) | Slot start → slot start + 15 min |
| Group auto-cancel | [groupBookingService.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/services/groupBookingService.js) | Unfilled groups cancelled 4 hours before slot |
| Domain restriction | [authController.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/controllers/authController.js) | Registration requires `@iitk.ac.in` email |
| Slot generation | [slotGeneratorService.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/services/slotGeneratorService.js) | Forward slots for next 3 days |
| Subscription plans | [subscriptionService.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/services/subscriptionService.js) | Monthly=30d, Semesterly=180d, Yearly=365d |
| Pass ID format | [subscriptionService.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/services/subscriptionService.js) | `GYM-YYYY-NNN` or `POOL-YYYY-NNN` |
| QR token expiry | [qrService.js](file:///c:/Users/HP/Patang/backend/src/services/qrService.js) | 24 hours (booking QR) |

