## 6. Key Workflows

### 6.1 User Authentication Flow
```
Register (email@iitk.ac.in + password)
  → Create unverified User + generate 6-digit OTP
  → Send OTP via Nodemailer
  → User submits OTP
  → isVerified=true, return JWT
  → Login: verify password → return JWT (30-day expiry)
```

### 6.2 Slot Booking Flow (V2)
```
GET /api/slot-booking/sports → fetch facilities, slot templates, capacity
  → Check suspension status
  → Check fair-use quota (≤2 in 72h)
  → POST /api/v2/bookings → validate facility + slot
    → Optimistic concurrency: slot Available→Booked
    → Create Booking (Confirmed or Provisioned for group)
    → Generate JWT-based QR token
  → At facility: POST .../check-in → caretaker scans QR
    → Validate window (slot start → +15 min)
    → Mark Attended
  → If no check-in: cron job marks NoShow → penalty
```

### 6.3 Subscription + QR Flow
```
GET /api/slot-booking/gym → plans, pricing, occupancy
  → POST /api/v2/subscriptions/apply (multipart: medicalCert + paymentReceipt)
    → Create SubscriptionV2 (status: Pending)
  → Admin: GET /api/v2/admin/subscriptions (scoped by facility type)
    → PATCH .../approve → generate passId + QR data URL
  → At facility: POST .../verify-entry (passId or QR payload)
    → Validate subscription active + date range
    → Auto-toggle entry/exit based on last action
    → Log AccessLog → update occupancy
```

### 6.4 Event Management Flow
```
Coordinator: POST /api/coordinator/events (+ optional poster)
  → Create Event (status: Pending)
  → Executive/Admin: GET /api/v2/admin/events/pending
    → PATCH .../approve|reject|requestChanges
  → Approved events appear in calendar + dashboard
```

### 6.5 Venue Booking Flow
```
Coordinator: GET /api/coordinator/venues?date=
  → POST /api/coordinator/venues (venueId, times, reason)
    → Overlap check → Create FacilityBlock (status: pending)
  → Executive approval needed (implied, but approval endpoint not implemented)
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Venue booking approval endpoint is missing.** The coordinator creates `FacilityBlock` with status `pending`, but there is no dedicated endpoint for executives to approve/reject venue booking requests. This is a gap.

### 6.6 Feedback Flow
```
User: POST /api/feedback → targetRole + subject + message + isAnonymous
  → Staff: GET /api/feedback/inbox (filtered by their roles)
    → Anonymous submissions have user details stripped
  → PATCH .../reply → status update + adminReply
```

